{"tid":1690252,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"食完tg [絲入]","createTime":"2019-11-03T08:30:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T05:56:43.000Z","uid":202296,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4a9de0882f9f075d1c9ebd89ff85b211c3c4cf2c","tid":1690252,"uid":202296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T08:30:22.000Z","msg":"近排隻大陸野tg真係好毒，<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食完會即晚嚟m，又少又黑，仲要斷斷續續咁<br />\n例如禮拜日食完tg，禮拜1去到禮拜4就會斷斷續續咁嚟<br />\n近排索完大陸野之後嗰個禮拜都喺咁，身體差咗勁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想問下除咗睇醫生之外，仲有咩可以改善，例如食啲咩飲啲咩，我驚未捱到光復嗰日，已經中毒死撚咗，你都知架啦，嗰個禮拜咁樣索山埃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n曱甴平，習曱甴，曱近平<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6cfa62b5020fc78cb7d7991bd2f51ea139d90ac","tid":1690252,"uid":210683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T08:31:52.000Z","msg":"幫你推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f74d03cc04c448c3e0c64912a2473f7c137859b","tid":1690252,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T08:35:47.000Z","msg":"帶豬咀都冇用?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaade3df28b2095d1958dfa6da4dc61f39179b30","tid":1690252,"uid":69472,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T08:40:59.000Z","msg":"要睇中醫調理下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搵國難忠醫幫手啦 唔好拖"},{"pid":"6df9946524fe86bc12399de6f7b5c1325f3b5d43","tid":1690252,"uid":155781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T08:42:28.000Z","msg":"睇中醫"},{"pid":"50776d3c0990788ee47f9d43956b83d039a9fb27","tid":1690252,"uid":239469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T08:43:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"89e9adadbe20b395c308099eee2c1d496696cda2","tid":1690252,"uid":235477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T08:46:06.000Z","msg":"要搞搞佢 <br />\n好撚認真"},{"pid":"6816d7db0f74914abcb72a6aea2063e9c48885a5","tid":1690252,"uid":82940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T08:48:12.000Z","msg":"推 曱甴平"},{"pid":"de5ca773213e88ef86ac905e8603dfc61bf05691","tid":1690252,"uid":119017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T08:49:09.000Z","msg":"快d睇中醫"},{"pid":"2004b7b648a79487a33273636377b132de093b14","tid":1690252,"uid":89641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T08:53:27.000Z","msg":"唔係絲偷睇完想講，大便深黑同茶色尿最少連續3日先會鮮色返。<br />\n<br />\n利申：ip唔洗check果區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n得閒既去睇中醫解解毒"},{"pid":"579b1488ea2fb09ca1e9bfedca6ddaf2d9a6f023","tid":1690252,"uid":29204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T08:56:14.000Z","msg":"快啲去睇中醫調理 <br />\n記得淨係講病徵唔好話自己食左tg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea0d9e2bcddceb1cd172bd7a2eae24b07e008d58","tid":1690252,"uid":123704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T08:59:35.000Z","msg":"幫推，身體好緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c231652921c821cc94e689150ed26460eec035e1","tid":1690252,"uid":126005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T09:32:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ad9a78e3548dd4ac933f46a5226590606c57eeaf","tid":1690252,"uid":176121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T09:34:29.000Z","msg":"國難忠醫 - 網上查詢 X 上門診治 X 派藥支援 <br />\nChannel link: <a href=\"https://t.me/findcmed\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffindcmed&d=AnzAvEp6rraOVT5%2FQxAiQXvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=e38822b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/findcmed</a><br />\n<br />\n1. 網上查詢<br />\n若發夢後身體出現任何不適，但由於醫護白色恐怖未能接受治療，歡迎先聯絡我地，視情況網上診斷、開方。<br />\n<br />\n以下為網上查詢Tg:<br />\n@mktkirara （網上診治）<br />\n@wteverittakess （網上診治）<br />\n@hkyeung （網上診治）<br />\n@h8k46 （網上診治 ）<br />\n@MSMbbb（網上診治 ）<br />\n@poopoodada （安排醫師）<br />\n@THYinnnnnnn （安排醫師）<br />\n@wtfairyec （安排醫師）<br />\n@zo_bbg （安排醫師）<br />\n@bambooy （安排醫師） <br />\n@twtcm (新）<br />\n@koosir123 （新）<br />\n@saabmmky （新）<br />\n@hellokittiii（新）<br />\n<br />\n(約五分鐘內沒有回覆，請找另一位，搵邊位隨緣即可）<br />\n_<br />\n<br />\n2. 上門診症 / 義診所  (由網上查詢分流)<br />\n若症狀複雜，未能透過網上查詢處理，將會視閣下意願，推薦最接近的義診所或安排上門診治<br />\n<br />\n中醫亦可處理跌打扭傷、內科、皮膚等多種問題，亦可選用中藥 / 針灸 / 正骨 等多種方法解決問題<br />\n<br />\n大部份醫師都係免費幫大家睇<br />\n如果用左錢係診斷/藥費<br />\n憑單搵我地Claim番就得<br />\n<br />\nClaim診金/藥費，請聯絡 @carriedothistoo <br />\n(比單、醫師TgUsername、閣下Payme QRcode, 文件齊全，幾分鐘內轉帳）<br />\n_<br />\n<br />\n3. 派藥支援<br />\n我們會定期製作中藥止咳沖劑，交予物資站 及 First Aider，務求 病向淺中醫，避免病情惡化<br />\n<br />\n所用中藥藥性平和，適合大部分人飲用，只需分辨初起咳嗽或久咳即可。<br />\n（G6PD患者亦可飲用，個別中藥敏感人士，建議先查詢後服用）<br />\n<br />\n其他咳嗽外症狀，歡迎查詢。<br />\n_<br />\n<br />\n4.前線經濟支援<br />\n我們明白部份前線可能因為發夢，而被經濟封鎖或漸漸面對經濟壓力<br />\n<br />\n我們會盡力提供臨時工作予各位追夢者，以解燃眉之急<br />\n<br />\n-<br />\n<br />\n5.「你諗橋&middot;我集資」計劃<br />\n我們明白你或許有大量有趣想法，想化為現實，偏偏卡係資金問題上，導致想法未能實現。 <br />\n<br />\n不妨試下將計劃，寫成計劃書，然後交比我地，將就可行性、意義、受眾多少等角度審批計劃書，及撥款支持。<br />\n<br />\n計劃書 請交比： @carriedothistoo"},{"pid":"f0d9dab4192333190a2e2d71c41da9bf2e248b2d","tid":1690252,"uid":202296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f74d03cc04c448c3e0c64912a2473f7c137859b","tid":1690252,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T08:35:47.000Z","msg":"帶豬咀都冇用?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:51:46.000Z","msg":"以前就得<br />\n依家唔撚得啦<br />\n啲野咁毒"},{"pid":"55d3b60173de65839f55eae5b08fab57bb69fd67","tid":1690252,"uid":202296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:53:50.000Z","m